About Sarasota Bay
About Sarasota Bay RV Park
Conveniently located in the heart of the Suncoast, our park is just minutes from premier shopping, top-notch golf courses, and stunning public beaches. Designed exclusively for guests 55 and older, and with a strict “no pet” policy, we guarantee a tranquil and enjoyable environment for all.
Our park features 240 spacious sites, each with concrete pads and full hook-ups, accommodating both 30 and 50 amp services. With a typical site width of 25 feet, you’ll have plenty of space to relax and unwind. Enjoy our exceptional amenities, including a heated pool, a well-appointed rec hall, and a professional shuffleboard court.
Experience the perfect blend of relaxation, community, and convenience at Sarasota Bay RV Park.
Book your stay today and start living Life by the Bay!
Sarasota Bay RV Park Views
Immerse yourself in stunning ocean vistas and vibrant park life at Sarasota Bay RV Park. Enjoy breathtaking views of Sarasota Bay and Anna Maria Island, all while engaging in a variety of activities. From peaceful beach walks and swimming in our heated pool to participating in community events, our park offers the perfect blend of relaxation and excitement amidst a picturesque setting.
